Job Description
Admin & Reception expertise : To assist MD in all administrative and organizational matters in an efficient and effective manner.
Arrange meetings and manage calendar scheduling for the section head and coordinate with concerned members and ensure attendance
in meetings
Organize arrange and prepare documentation for the meetings both internal & external to ensure follow up & dispatch of correspondence.
follow up messages issues record & relay accurate messages from clients on telephone e-mail provide adequate information when needed
reports to the Head & ensure projects on track. implement accurate database update maintain and store departmental files and departmental documentation maintain confidentiality
Skills
A level or equivalent, 1-2 yrs. of experience in administration .proficient in MS office packages Good communication skills in English
Change management, developing self and others drive for results working with people customer focus & talking responsibility
Proficient in MS Office
